{"tid":938354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孟晚舟微信首發文：以祖國為傲！","createTime":"2018-12-12T08:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T13:40:40.000Z","uid":75969,"like":8,"dislike":113,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"e289967c0091857b0fb20dc34e1e8756a6b44959","tid":938354,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T08:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181212/s00004/4f599f799ef798b27aa90b8c2e8b3639.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181212%2Fs00004%2F4f599f799ef798b27aa90b8c2e8b3639.jpg&h=296f356f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為首席財務官孟晚舟，獲准以1000萬加元資產等條件保釋外出。孟晚舟離開加拿大卑詩省最高法院時，未有回應傳媒提問，但她在本港時間下午於微信朋友圈留言，「我在溫哥華，已回到家人身邊。我以華為為傲，我以祖國為傲！謝謝每一位關心我的人」，並附上寫有「偉大的背後都是苦難」、印有華為標誌的圖片。<br />\n<br />\n孟晚舟保釋條件包括1000萬加元保釋金、孟晚舟丈夫劉曉棕和另外至少5人擔保、交出所有護照、自行支付每天全日24小時監察費用，和穿戴電子腳環等，須於明年2月6日到法庭報到。另外，美國政府須於引渡申請限期內，亦即明年1月8日前，正式提交孟晚舟的引渡申請。<br />\n<br />\n（參考消息網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181212/s00004/1544603115073/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181212%2Fs00004%2F1544603115073%2F&d=f5cLTUp0JE4sC2jahDfC7v%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=6e71d5d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181212%2Fs00004%2F1544603115073%2F&h=511a9491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181212/s00004/1544603115073/</a>"},{"pid":"84aacc1c5d46f428c476272c555b23e284ae3530","tid":938354,"uid":41818,"like":184,"dislike":0,"score":184,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T08:51:28.000Z","msg":"係就帶晒你d蟲仔蟲女返支那住啦"},{"pid":"000239ed7f8038bbf519d2002976d14a5c2e1f15","tid":938354,"uid":41545,"like":164,"dislike":0,"score":164,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T08:54:45.000Z","msg":"祖國係加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wond